text: An image shared on Facebook purportedly shows President Donald Trump praising his response to the coronavirus pandemic on Twitter, saying, I have done a tremendous job. There are still more people alive then ( sic ) dead!
A viral Facebook post shared more than 65,000 times claims an MSNBC reporter said on-air, I hope enough people die from CoronaVirus that it harms Trump’s re-election.
An image shared on Facebook claims President Donald Trump said, The doctors said they’ve never seen a body kill the Coronavirus like my body.
